			<article id="post-1270" class="post-1270 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized tag-abrams-krochak tag-applications tag-backlog tag-canada tag-canada-family-sponsorship tag-canada-immigration tag-canada-immigration-partner tag-canada-immigration-sponsorship tag-canada-immigration-spouse tag-canada-visa tag-canadian-family-sponsorship tag-canadian-immigration tag-canadian-immigration-sponsorship tag-common-law tag-documentation tag-documents tag-family-class tag-fast-track tag-immigration-canada-sponsor tag-processing tag-processing-times tag-sponsor tag-sponsor-partner-canada tag-sponsor-spouse-canada tag-sponsorship tag-spousal-sponsorship tag-work-permit">

